        <updateDate>2008-12-23T16:57:48Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>National Debt Reduction Trust Fund Act of 2008 - Establishes in the Treasury the National Debt Reduction Trust Fund. Requires the Secretary of the Treasury to transfer to such Trust Fund revenues attributable to the exploration for, development of, or production of oil, natural gas, or oil shale located on federal lands in Alaska or the Outer Continental Shelf and to use such revenues to reduce the national debt. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
    <title>National Debt Reduction Trust Fund Act of 2008</title>
